{"tid":1913174,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[You are fake news ]質疑世衛3.4%死亡率「假的」 川普:應不到1% 染疫能上班","createTime":"2020-03-06T14:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T13:29:36.000Z","uid":20058,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"8e09103b10d2e484f54a4e8161ad28a4eb5fbce5","tid":1913174,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T14:48:44.000Z","msg":"美國總統川普質疑，世界衞生組織（WHO）對武漢肺炎疫情發放不準確數據，認為死亡率達3.4%的評估過高，又指感染武肺的人仍可安全地上班。<br />\n川普周三晚接受福斯新聞的電話直播訪問時說：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「我認為3.4%實在是一個虛假的數字。」他開始時說「這只是我的直覺」</span></span>，還表示「根據與很多相關人士的談話，很多人會感染，但它非常溫和 &ndash; 他們會很快康復，他們甚至不用求醫」。<br />\n川普指，很多只有輕微病徵的人，不會求醫或去醫院，他相信這類數字非常多，跟著提出自己推斷的死亡率，認為是1%以下。<br />\n記者周四早追問川普有關訪問內容，川普卻堅稱從沒有說過有病的人仍應該上班。他在推特發文，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">指這全是假新聞，是民主黨散播的假消息</span></span>。（國際中心／綜合外電報導） <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb6a14dd52660ba2fa1b4cda88f2a9a5b5e50452","tid":1913174,"uid":8014,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T14:50:48.000Z","msg":"cls 好撚on9<br />\n<br />\n抗疫仲玩政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c7c12cf5d23742bb91c84909a13c8eac70a604","tid":1913174,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T14:51:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/column/article/906/rnews/20200306/1713989/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fcolumn%2Farticle%2F906%2Frnews%2F20200306%2F1713989%2F&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnKf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=c708f434\" data-ef-url=\"h